<title>USA: TABLE - Melita Q2 pro forma net rises.</title>
<headline>TABLE - Melita Q2 pro forma net rises.</headline>
<dateline>NORCROSS, Ga. 1997-07-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Shr			  $0.29		    $0.17</p>
<p> Net			  3,728		    2,074</p>
<p> Revs			15,530		   11,886</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  12,868		   12,360</p>
<p>	  6  MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr			  $0.47		    $0.33</p>
<p> Net			  6,048		    4,114</p>
<p> Revs			30,199		   22,907</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  12,758		   12,360</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTES: This was company's first quarter since June initial public offering. Q2 1997 pro forma net was $1.7 million or $0.13 per share vs $1.3 million or $0.11. Six-months 1997 net was $3.1 million or $0.24 per share vs $2.6 million or $0.21.</p>
<p>1997 net income results include one-time $1.5 million benefit from deferred tax adjustment as result of company's change in status from &quot;S&quot; corporation to &quot;C&quot; corporation.</p>
<p>Full name of company is Melita International Corp.</p>
